{"tid":128250,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米MIX 惊現日本二手商店：售價幾乎翻倍","createTime":"2017-02-20T16:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T03:24:56.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15b8aaf3eb1ce01ba102765f72cea0dc6dc6baf7","tid":128250,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:04:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1268169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksilicon.com%2Farticles%2F1268169&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=30ade4e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1268169</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Xiaomi-Mix-Japan-2nd-hand.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FXiaomi-Mix-Japan-2nd-hand.jpg&h=61b0250f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日前這部話題機在日本有售！不過該部小米 Mix 出現的地方是當地的中古店 (即二手店)。從圖片中看到這個二手小米 Mix 屬於最高階的尊享版，規格方面：2K LCD 屏幕、&ldquo;滿血版&rdquo; Snapdragon 821 處理器、6GB RAM、256GB ROM、全陶瓷機身、超高屏幕佔用比率 (91.3%)。<br />\n<br />\n至於售價方面為 109,800 日元 (約 HK$7,492、NT$29,931)，相比小米官方價人民幣 3,999 元 (約 HK$4,511、NT$18,022) 高出不少。不過這個價錢的二手小米 Mix 能否賣得出，小編也有一定疑問。。。"},{"pid":"1dd8fc770d30a00d5136196c6494ee3592d90656","tid":128250,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"惊你老味咩"},{"pid":"7aaaf7e66d19299c3dcbeef2d028aea0614f01ec","tid":128250,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5266904b858cef890ce4151d118e7a597f04d549","tid":128250,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T02:30:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9422bc2f45a93aa81be4c4256b2d28928dd0668f","tid":128250,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T